134
00:09:43,997 --> 00:09:45,464
''No, l'm not.''

135
00:09:45,531 --> 00:09:47,795
That's the silliest thing
l ever heard.

136
00:09:47,867 --> 00:09:50,836
You've got a fine job
and you're engaged to a fine girl.

137
00:09:50,904 --> 00:09:53,873
You're lost in a fine forest.
What more do you want?

138
00:09:53,940 --> 00:09:57,899
l don't know.
Something seems wrong.

139
00:09:57,977 --> 00:10:00,104
Especially about Jane and me.

140
00:10:00,179 --> 00:10:02,807
That makes everything seem wrong.

141
