school in Edinburgh and now Jean--

278
00:19:50,870 --> 00:19:52,701
and l've got nothing.

279
00:19:52,771 --> 00:19:56,571
Nothing but to be trapped
in this peasant village all my life.

280
00:19:56,642 --> 00:19:59,008
Look at it.
The boundaries of a town?

281
00:20:00,112 --> 00:20:02,205
Not to me.

282
00:20:02,281 --> 00:20:05,614
