356
00:25:33,312 --> 00:25:35,542
l hope he knows
how grateful l am to him...

357
00:25:35,614 --> 00:25:37,377
to postponin' the miracle for me.

358
00:25:37,449 --> 00:25:40,213
''-That what?
-'Tis a toast we have here, sir.''

359
00:25:40,285 --> 00:25:43,686
And may God bless me this evenin'
as much as l would bless him...

360
00:25:43,755 --> 00:25:47,350
