lt only shuts ya off more
from the world...

567
00:44:34,251 --> 00:44:37,414
and this is only a cursed town
if ya make it so.

568
00:44:37,488 --> 00:44:40,389
''To the rest of us,
'tis a blessed place.''

569
00:44:56,807 --> 00:44:58,138
