There's plenty--

640
00:50:01,645 --> 00:50:03,579
What is it?
What frightened you?

641
00:50:03,647 --> 00:50:05,638
'Tis nothin'.

642
00:50:05,716 --> 00:50:09,208
ls it the bridge? Why do you have
such a look of fear on your face?

643
00:50:09,286 --> 00:50:10,583
l cannot say.

644
00:50:11,655 --> 00:50:13,589
Why can't you?

645
00:50:13,657 --> 00:50:17,753
''Fiona, what's the matter?
What's going on around here?''

646
00:50:19,029 --> 00:50:21,497
What was all that business
about Charlie and a miracle?

647
00:50:58,969 --> 00:51:02,564
''Hey, look out! Tommy!''

648
00:51:02,639 --> 00:51:04,732
What happened? Tommy!

649
00:51:04,808 --> 00:51:06,400
Are you all right?

650
00:51:13,951 --> 00:51:18,217
''lf there's anything l hate,
it's you.''

651
00:51:18,288 --> 00:51:20,950
Any civilized person
would be dead by now.

652
00:51:22,359 --> 00:51:26,261
Maybe the sun
gave me the power

653
00:51:26,330 --> 00:51:31,267
For l could swim Loch Lomond
and be home in half an hour

654
00:51:31,335 --> 00:51:35,465
